mimi.db.minions["Tasuil"] = { ["earth"]="", ["wind"]="7", ["fire"]="", ["water"]="", ["life"]="", ["death"]="", ["hunting"]="18", ["diplomacy"]="", ["harvesting"]="", ["dimension"]="15", ["artifact"]="15", ["assasination"]="", ["max attribute score"]="25", ["max stamina"]="30", ['obtained']='Hidden Minion', ['details']='Tasuil minion starts with 12 stamina and has 4 attributes: Life, Diplomacy, Harvesting and Artifact\nObtaining the Minion Card: Tasuil\n1. Obtain Minion Card: Una and Minion Card: Rirnef. Una is gained from RIFT Store -> Pets -> Minions once you are Friendly with the Onir faction/notoriety. Rirnef is gained from \'Questionable Allegiance\' quest in Port Scuddra.\n2. Go on 5/15min adventure deck missions until you find some chained missions with the \'hush\' graphic background. Once you do a few of those, you\'ll find unchained mission that says that you can only do the mission if you don\'t have x minion card.\n3. The 6 minions are:\n3.a. Pyrestorm - Chance drop from Goboro Reef rare \'Pyrestorm\'.\n3.b. Orlan - Chance drop from hidden chest or rare \'Blightbeard\' from the Chronicle Intrepid: Greenscale\'s Blight\n3.c. Quaq - Chance drop from completing \'The Leviathan\' zone event in Tyrant\'s Throne.\n3.d. Lil Reggie - Chance drop from Nightmare Rift caches.\n3.e. Ionraic - Chance drop from Instant Adventure Caches.\n3.f. C1-0N3 - Crafted by Apothecaries. Recipe can be found under RIFT Store -> Crafting -> Apothecaries -> filter: minion.\n4. Once you have all 6 cards, you will begin a new adventure chain starting with \'Your Team is Assembled!\' in the 5min/15min deck.\n5. Keep doing the 5min/15min deck whilst leveling up your 6 minions to Level 10 or above. This will allow you to continue on the chain.\n6. Eventually you\'ll see missions that are not part of the chain that can only be completed by C1-0N3 or Quaq. You must send these cards on both missions and keep them in your active minion slots.\n7. When you have both C1-0N3 and Quaq out on these non-chain adventures (that still have the \'hush\' background), you can then obtain \'Guards Tricked Inot Dungeon, Door Sealed\'.\n8. Similar adventures occur where you need to have Lil Reggie and Pyrestorm on their active adventures, and Orlan and Ionraic on their active adventure.\n9. Eventually, you\'ll get \'Rescue Tasuil, Dragon of Telara\' mission. Completing this mission rewards you with the Minion Card: Tasuil.\n\nNote: All these missions are in the 5min/15min adventure deck.\nThanks to Turntablist, Avocados, Muspel and Crithappens for researching and experimenting to complete this chain.\nAlso a big thanks to Avocados for providing a great guide on how to obtain the Tasuil minion card that you can find below:\nhttp://www.reddit.com/r/Rift/comments/2x0twk/guide_tasuil_minion_card/',  }
